    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my reliable ride! It's in really solid shape and has been such a joy to drive\u2014super dependable and ready for many more adventures. I've taken great care of it, and it's looking for someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. I\u2019m offering a great price for a quick sale, so come by and take it for a spin! I'd love to see it go to a good home.",
      "price": 29500.0,
