    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. This unit excels in mechanical health, with the high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies performing flawlessly. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory rigidity with the M-Variable differential providing exceptional lock-up under cornering loads. While the exterior displays some honest road patina consistent with its 'good' status, the suspension geometry remains true and the engine's power band is as linear and visceral as ever. A mechanically robust specimen for the enthusiast who values performance over concours perfection.",
